Splunk Jobs Monitoring
----------------------------------------
Author: Shailesh
Version/Date: 1.0/03-19-2018

Using this app:
----------------------------------------

ABOUT
------
This app helps identify for users , dashboards and searches that are causing slow performance on splunk. Since splunk admin do not have control on what searches users are writing , it helps to check which search or dashboard is causing issue . How many other searches are impacted by this issue.


INSTALLATION
-------------
Install this app on Splunk search heads.
